                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980418-90-victim756 t17980418-90-viclabel476"></join>: I was coming out of the <placeName id="t17980418-90-crimeloc477">Chamberlain's Office, Guildhall</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17980418-90-crimeloc477" type="placeName" value="Chamberlain's Office, Guildhall"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17980418-90-crimeloc477" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980418-90-off474 t17980418-90-crimeloc477"></join>, I do not recollect the day, when I put my hand in my pocket and missed my handkerchief; I saw the prisoner near me, I followed him round Guildhall yard, I stopped him, and charged him with it; he denied it at first, but afterwards produced my handkerchief; there was no mark upon it, but from the general appearance of it, I believe it to be my handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17980418-90-person758">
                  JOHN
                   TURNER
