             sworn. - I am a constable, (produces the handkerchief): I received it from the prosecutor, or rather between him and the prisoner; I have had it ever since. I searched him at the office, and found two others.</p>
               <p>Hill. This is my handkerchief.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I did not pick his pocket.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called two witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>
